    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please Smile! 一款为鼠标和键盘优化的3D平台游戏！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>100% 游戏体验！</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验60个难度逐渐增加的房间！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无语言障碍，无过场动画，无中断！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>令人兴奋的能力！</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >停止或倒转时间！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/206403d5109fa856f22a38853c28ee36.poster.avif?t=1734007004\" width=450 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/206403d5109fa856f22a38853c28ee36.webm?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/206403d5109fa856f22a38853c28ee36.mp4?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在两个状态之间切换平台区域！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/8eba9e4e35b370ee2f288fffbbe6e48b.poster.avif?t=1734007004\" width=450 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/8eba9e4e35b370ee2f288fffbbe6e48b.webm?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/8eba9e4e35b370ee2f288fffbbe6e48b.mp4?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用冲刺到达遥远的平台！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/0173cd0d6422cd2453f18d57138ef8ad.poster.avif?t=1734007004\" width=450 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/0173cd0d6422cd2453f18d57138ef8ad.webm?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/0173cd0d6422cd2453f18d57138ef8ad.mp4?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将重力引导到新的物体上！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/f67cb929e6d2363cab6a064aa8493c3f.poster.avif?t=1734007004\" width=450 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/f67cb929e6d2363cab6a064aa8493c3f.webm?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/f67cb929e6d2363cab6a064aa8493c3f.mp4?t=1734007004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射击目标，从远处改变世界！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/644afde500b252af1345e5689121fa02.avif?t=1734007004\" width=600 height=330 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>没有敌人，尽享多样化！</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使没有敌人也不会感到无聊！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个房间都有自己的独特创意！从隐形平台到充满秘密的创意场景。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/d756c8bef6466e5a203b8177129d65d9.poster.avif?t=1734007004\" width=450 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106620/extras/d756c8bef6466e5a2